ur wedding celebration. Please arrive promptly as the yacht will be leaving the dock at 4:30 pm and we want you on board!”</p>		\n										<img width=\"570\" height=\"810\" src=\"http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1893775_1324903-my-name-first.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1893775_1324903-my-name-first.png 570w, http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1893775_1324903-my-name-first-211x300.png 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" />											\n			<h2>RSVP Here:</h2>		\n<form action=\"/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php#wpcf7-f83-o1\" method=\"post\" novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"83\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"5.0.3\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"en_US\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f83-o1\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_container_post\" value=\"0\" />\n<p><label> Please enter the full names of all family members included in this RSVP (required)<br />\n    <input type=\"text\" name=\"your-name\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" /> </label></p>\n<p><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"checkbox-735\" value=\"ACCEPT WITH PLEASURE\" />ACCEPT WITH PLEASURE<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"checkbox-735\" value=\"DECLINE WITH REGRET\" />DECLINE WITH REGRET</p>\n<p><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Send\" /></p>\n</form>                \n			<ul id=\"eael-countdown-1c5ad7b\" data-date=\"Dec 23 2018 15:30:00\">\n			    <li>00Days</li>			    <li>00Hours</li>			   <li>00Minutes</li>			   <li>00Seconds</li>			</ul>','Invitation & RSVP','','publish','closed','closed','','wedding-invitation','','','2018-08-14 20:01:10','2018-08-14 20:01:10','',0,'http://hibaandwaseem.com/?page_id=22',0,'page','',0),(23,1,'2018-08-12 13:26:02','2018-08-12 13:26:02','','Wedding Invitation','','inherit','closed','closed','','22-revision-v1','','','2018-08-12 13:26:02','2018-08-12 13:26:02','',22,'http://hibaandwaseem.com/22-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(226,1,'2018-12-11 18:12:52','2018-12-11 18:12:52','<a href=\"https://forecast7.com/en/27d95n82d46/tampa/?unit=us\" data-label_1=\"TAMPA\" data-label_2=\"WEATHER\" data-theme=\"clear\" >TAMPA WEATHER</a>','Weather','','inherit','closed','closed','','214-revision-v1','','','2018-12-11 18:12:52','2018-12-11 18:12:52','',214,'http://hibaandwaseem.com/214-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(198,1,'2018-08-27 21:32:40','2018-08-27 21:32:40','[timeline-express]','Wedding Itinerary','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2018-08-27 21:32:40','2018-08-27 21:32:40','',15,'http://hibaandwaseem.com/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2018-08-12 13:22:42','2018-08-12 13:22:42','<h3>Family and Friends,</h3>		\n		<p>We are excited to celebrate our wedding with you on the 23rd of December, 2018. We hope you enjoy the nice, slightly chilly, Florida weather aboard the StarShip II Yacht in Tampa, FL. Bring a light sweater.</p><p>While we love to watch children run and play, this is an adults only kind of day!</p><p>Girls, dress up and let your hair down, there are two decks and we get a whole one all to ourselves!</p><p>Please don\'t hesitate to ask us anything on your mind. We can\'t wait to see you all soon!</p><p>- Hiba &amp; Waseem</p><p>P.S. This website was built by yours truly (Hiba) :)</p>		\n										<img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_2882-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_2882-683x1024.jpg 683w, http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_2882-200x300.jpg 200w, http://hibaandwaseem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_2882-768x1152.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" />','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2018-12-11 18:06:11','2018-12-11 18:06:11','',0,'http://hibaandwaseem.com/?